OL,4,Cunmarked lorry
OL,6,FUndercover police officers patrolling
OL,7,FWest Yorkshire's motorways in an
OL,8,Funmarked lorry have caught dozens of
OL,9,Fdrivers breaking the law.
OL,11,FThe forces road policing unit used a
OL,12,Fspecially adapted vehicle, using the
OL,13,Felevated position to observe and film
OL,14,Fother drivers.
OL,16,FSeat belt, mobile phone and speeding
OL,17,Foffences were among the 48 incidents
OL,18,Fcaptured on the lorry's camera.
