OL,6,FTwo drivers were also arrested for
OL,7,Fdriving without due care and attention
OL,8,Fwhilst another driver was arrested for
OL,9,Fbeing under the influence of drugs or
OL,10,Fdrink.
OL,12,FOfficers say that once an offence was
OL,13,Fseen the vehicle was then intercepted
OL,14,Fby a marked police car.
OL,16,FSgt Ryan Burt of the Roads Policing
OL,17,FUnit said: "The elevated position of
OL,18,Fthe cab allowed us to capture footage
OL,19,Fof some really poor and potentially
OL,20,Fdangerous driving and make some
OL,21,Feffective interventions."
